## Smart Messages (Nudge) System

**4 nudges per model**, segmented by spend tier. Priority trigger: "Fan Comes Online."

| SM | Audience | Tone | Approach |
|---|---|---|---|
| VIP | Whale+Shark ($400+) | GFE warm, "I missed you" | Connection → chatter takes over |
| MID | Shrimp+Low ($30-400) | Flirty + curiosity | Spark interest → session push |
| LOW | Rats ($1-30) | Direct hooks, no fluff | Activate → quick qualification |
| ZERO | $0 fans | Provocative + direct sale | PPV $3-5 attached, break $0 barrier |

**Key rule:** ZERO fans get DIRECT SALE, not GFE. No emotional investment exists. Send low-price PPV or free teaser directly in the nudge.

